short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension powers Websee, the most popular daily links and discussions across the web, from anonymous extension users like you!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
